Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我原本打算娓娓道来  但我说出来了\N{\r原文字幕}I was gonna build up to that.  But, uh... there it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是你未来的妻子\N{\r原文字幕}I'm your future wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-谁说的?  -你啊\N{\r原文字幕}-Who said it?  -You do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你告诉我的\N{\r原文字幕}You told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你向我解释  你是从我们已婚的未来里过来的\N{\r原文字幕}You explained,  you were visiting me from a time in the future,  when we're married.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉,我不是故意突然说这些\N{\r原文字幕}I'm sorry, I--I don't mean to,  uh, spring it on you like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过在未来我们是一对已婚夫妻\N{\r原文字幕}but, in the future,  we're a married couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜\N{\r原文字幕}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么恭喜?\N{\r原文字幕}-Seriously? Congratulations?  -What--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.26,0:17:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然我该说什么?\N{\r原文字幕}-What am I supposed to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你太看得起自己了吧?  -我甚至不知道要回答什么‥\N{\r原文字幕}-Ah, you don't think much of yourself, do you? I don't know,  I can't even begin to answer  something like--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-恭喜是怎样?  -这场对话没有前情提要\N{\r原文字幕}-"Congratulations" though?  -There is literally no precedent -for this conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-当然啊  -抱歉,要消化的讯息太多了\N{\r原文字幕}-That's for sure. I'm sorry, it's just a lot to-- to process.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,握着我的手再开口\N{\r原文字幕}Take my hand  when you say process.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.99,0:17:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-说真的,结婚?  -没错\N{\r原文字幕}-I've been married?  -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.45,0:17:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你是我的‥  -我就是\N{\r原文字幕}-You're my...  -Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.74,0:17:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你是我的妻子?  -没错,你未来的妻子\N{\r原文字幕}-You're my wife?  -Your future wife. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们四小时前才认识  我们甚至还没点餐\N{\r原文字幕}I met you four hours ago,  we haven't even ordered yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道‥我真的明白‥\N{\r原文字幕}I know. I know. I do.  I mean I--I get it. I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说已经十四年了\N{\r原文字幕}It's like  14 years for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说却只是今天的事\N{\r原文字幕}Just earlier today for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-真的让人难以接受  -没错\N{\r原文字幕}it's--it's a lot. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以问我问题吧\N{\r原文字幕}So, ask me questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧,那么‥\N{\r原文字幕}Okay, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然我们会结婚\N{\r原文字幕}Seeing as we're gonna  be married, and, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且无意冒犯  这只是你的片面之词‥\N{\r原文字幕}no offence, I've only got  your word for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,严格来说  我之前也只有你的片面之词\N{\r原文字幕}Well, technically, I've only got  your word for that,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你若仔细想想  夫妻之间还能有什么呢?\N{\r原文字幕}but, if you think about it  what does any couple ever have--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:17:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-拜托别那样  -哪样?\N{\r原文字幕}-Please, don't do that.  -Do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.70,0:18:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-在我提到夫妻时咽口水  -我咽口水了吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Swallow, when I say  the word "couple."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错,而且还发出声音  隔壁桌都看过来了\N{\r原文字幕}-Did I just swallow?  -Yeah, audibly. -The next table looked over.  -Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧\N{\r原文字幕}So, come on,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问问题吧\N{\r原文字幕}questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.71,0:18:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们怎么认识的?\N{\r原文字幕}How did we meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是问对我来说是怎么样吗?\N{\r原文字幕}You mean, how was it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马克‥是你吗?\N{\r原文字幕}CLARE, 6: Mark. Mark, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的地盘,你不该来这里\N{\r原文字幕}This is my place. You're not supposed  to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好,克蕾儿\N{\r原文字幕}Hello, Clare.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.56,0:19:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你是谁?  -亨利啊\N{\r原文字幕}-Who are you?  -Well, it's Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亨利?\N{\r原文字幕}Henry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:20:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对,我只是觉得不舒服\N{\r原文字幕}Yeah, I'm just, uh,  being sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旅行有时会让我不舒服  你知道的\N{\r原文字幕}Travelling makes me sick  sometimes, you know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁?\N{\r原文字幕}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还不认识我吗,克蕾儿?  我们还没有见过?\N{\r原文字幕}Uh, don't you  know me yet, Clare? Haven't we met yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-没有  -好吧,没关系‥\N{\r原文字幕}-No.  -Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你现在认识我了  你知道我是你朋友\N{\r原文字幕}That's okay. That's okay.  Uh, 'cause you're meeting me now and you know I'm a friend, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我保证我是你的朋友  我叫亨利\N{\r原文字幕}I promise you I'm a friend.  My name's Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有叫亨利的朋友\N{\r原文字幕}I don't have any friends  called Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你现在有了\N{\r原文字幕}Well, you do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我个忙  拿些衣服给我,好吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Hey, could you do me a favor  and go and get me some clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-为什么?  -因为我没有衣服\N{\r原文字幕}Why?  'Cause I don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我敢打赌你很会选衣服\N{\r原文字幕}And I bet you are amazing  at choosing clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.53,0:20:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么在室内奔跑呢?\N{\r原文字幕}What's all this  running around indoors?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.49,0:20:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奈尔,你知道想象中的朋友吧?\N{\r原文字幕}Nell, you know  what an imaginary friend is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-知道  -我在林子里找到了一个\N{\r原文字幕}-True.  -I found one in the woods
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.79,0:20:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在要为他着装  因为他全身光溜溜\N{\r原文字幕}and I'm gonna dress him up  'cause he's naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:20:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你好啊  -你好\N{\r原文字幕}-CLARE, 6: Hi.  -Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是这里  -对,只要打上地轴就可以了\N{\r原文字幕}So, right there. Yeah, just label it,  Earth's axis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的,地轴\N{\r原文字幕}Oh, okay. Earth's axis.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.54,0:22:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我准备好了\N{\r原文字幕}Okay, I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.09,0:22:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你动作真快\N{\r原文字幕}-CLARE, 6: That was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.46,0:22:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的经验可多了呢\N{\r原文字幕}-I've had a lot of practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.55,0:22:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在流血\N{\r原文字幕}You're bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.93,0:22:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟你朝我丢了鞋子\N{\r原文字幕}-Well, you threw a shoe at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我不会道歉  -你为何要道歉?\N{\r原文字幕}-I'm not saying sorry. Why should you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.72,0:22:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那是什么印子?  -那个只是胎记\N{\r原文字幕}What's that mark? Oh, that?  That's just a birthmark.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.60,0:22:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心,不会痛\N{\r原文字幕}Don't worry, it doesn't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.73,0:22:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来就像你踩烂了一颗草莓\N{\r原文字幕}It looks like you stood  on a strawberry and squished it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.65,0:22:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别人也说过‥不对\N{\r原文字幕}Someone else said that. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.78,0:22:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-哪里不对?  -不是别人说的\N{\r原文字幕}-What's wrong?  -Well, it wasn't someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,0:22:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你见过恐龙吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Have you seen dinosaurs?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.50,0:22:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有次搔了恐龙的肚子\N{\r原文字幕}I tickled  a dinosaur's tummy once.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.96,0:23:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实是两次  但那是在自然历史博物馆的事\N{\r原文字幕}Twice actually, but it was  in the Natural History Museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.83,0:23:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的恐龙啦\N{\r原文字幕}Real ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.71,0:23:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会时空旅行  但不会到那么远的过去\N{\r原文字幕}Well, I travel in time,  but not that far back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我通常会到我出生后的时间里\N{\r原文字幕}I tend to stay in the same time  since I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.72,0:23:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不就是有恐龙吗?\N{\r原文字幕}-Is that not dinosaurs?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.84,0:23:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是,克蕾儿,没有恐龙\N{\r原文字幕}-No, Clare. That is not dinosaurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.10,0:23:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你未来有小孩吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Do you have kids in the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕没有\N{\r原文字幕}No. I'm afraid not.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.11,0:23:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你有妻子吗?  -有啊\N{\r原文字幕}Do you have a wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.27,0:23:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-她漂亮吗?  -她非常漂亮\N{\r原文字幕}-Yeah  -Is she pretty? -She's very pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.24,0:23:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她叫什么名字?\N{\r原文字幕}-What's her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.95,0:23:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好笑的是她叫克蕾儿\N{\r原文字幕}Well, funnily enough,  her name's Clare.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.74,0:23:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-和我一样  -对,和你一样\N{\r原文字幕}-Like me.  -Yeah. Like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.53,0:23:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是一见钟情吗?  -天啊,最好不要\N{\r原文字幕}Was it love at first sight? -God, I hope not.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.00,0:23:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会亲她吗?\N{\r原文字幕}-Do you kiss her?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.83,0:23:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我会  -为什么?\N{\r原文字幕}-Uh... ...yeah.  -Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.54,0:23:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为感觉很好也因为我爱她\N{\r原文字幕}Because it's nice,  and because I love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.55,0:23:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你喜欢亲人?\N{\r原文字幕}Why do you like kissing people?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.51,0:23:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要为你的马刷毛?\N{\r原文字幕}Why do you like brushing  your horse's hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.39,0:23:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在刷毛,是梳毛\N{\r原文字幕}It's not brushing,  I'm grooming her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.93,0:24:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了,换个话题,克蕾儿\N{\r原文字幕}Okay, moving on. Uh, Clare,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.68,0:24:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再过不久我就要消失了\N{\r原文字幕}in a little while,  I'm gonna disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.19,0:24:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我能看吗?  -可以\N{\r原文字幕}-Can I watch?  -Yeah, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.11,0:24:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我要你帮我个忙\N{\r原文字幕}But I'd like you to do me  a little favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.52,0:24:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走的时候会留下衣服\N{\r原文字幕}See when I go, I'm gonna leave  my clothes behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.48,0:24:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要你把它们拿走  收在安全的地方\N{\r原文字幕}But I'd like you to take them,  and put them somewhere safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.86,0:24:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许收在这个石头下\N{\r原文字幕}Maybe, um, under this rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.53,0:24:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是收在盒子里  衣服就能保持干燥\N{\r原文字幕}And if you could put them  in a box for me, -they'll be nice and dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.07,0:24:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会回来吗?\N{\r原文字幕} -Are you coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.58,0:24:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会啊,我会回来很多次\N{\r原文字幕}Yeah, I'll be back  lots of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.00,0:24:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说我已经回来过几次了\N{\r原文字幕}Some of those times  have already happened for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.96,0:24:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会发现我看起来  比较年轻或比较老\N{\r原文字幕}you'll see me looking younger.  Maybe older.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.71,0:24:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能带着自己的衣服吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Can't you bring  your own clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.71,0:24:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能带任何东西,这是规则\N{\r原文字幕}I can't bring anything.  Those are the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.96,0:24:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会有规则?\N{\r原文字幕}Why are there rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.92,0:24:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我不知道  -谁告诉你这些规则的?\N{\r原文字幕}-I don't know.  -Who told you the rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.13,0:24:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你的问题可真多  -你说我能问的\N{\r原文字幕}You ask a lot of questions,  don't you? -You said I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.76,0:24:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次时空旅行时  遇到一个‥男人\N{\r原文字幕}-Well, the very first time  it happened to me, -there was, uh, a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.06,0:24:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是谁啊?  -另一个‥\N{\r原文字幕}-Who? Another...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.14,0:24:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一个时空旅人  但是说来话长,克蕾儿\N{\r原文字幕}another time traveler, but,  it's a very long story, Clare.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.90,0:24:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好,我喜欢听故事\N{\r原文字幕}Good. I like stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.53,0:24:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧,亨利,快要关门了\N{\r原文字幕}Come on, Henry.  It's closing in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.24,0:25:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-菲尔德自然史博物馆即将闭馆  -来吧,我们走吧\N{\r原文字幕}And Chicago's... Come on, you two. Let's go. We will be closing shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.46,0:25:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\r原文字幕}-Ah!  -Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.29,0:25:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亨利,觉得如何?  第一次来博物馆,喜欢吗?\N{\r原文字幕}What do you think, Henry?  First museum, you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.84,0:25:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他爱死了,你说是不是,亨利?\N{\r原文字幕}-Mm-hmm.  -Oh, he loved it. -Didn't you, Henry?  -Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.93,0:25:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我们能再去一次吗?  -当然可以\N{\r原文字幕}-Can we go back?  -Of course, we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.27,0:25:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚吗?\N{\r原文字幕}-Tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.81,0:25:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快就可以了\N{\r原文字幕}-Soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.32,0:25:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好睡觉\N{\r原文字幕}Sleep tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.59,0:25:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小子,亨利,穿上这个\N{\r原文字幕}Hey, kid! Henry. Put this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.97,0:26:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你时空旅行回到三小时前了\N{\r原文字幕}You've time traveled back,  about three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.64,0:26:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前面有个垃圾桶\N{\r原文字幕}There's a trash can  in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.18,0:26:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会这么说  是因为很快你就会觉得不舒服\N{\r原文字幕}Now, I say that because  in a minute, you're gonna be sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.69,0:26:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道我会不舒服?\N{\r原文字幕}How did you know I'd be sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.86,0:26:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是时空旅人\N{\r原文字幕}'Cause I'm a time traveler, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.95,0:26:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的经验可多了呢\N{\r原文字幕}I've had a lot of practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.08,0:26:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你会更吃惊\N{\r原文字幕}Thought you might look  a bit more surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.16,0:26:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对什么吃惊?\N{\r原文字幕}-About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.33,0:26:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然出现在这里\N{\r原文字幕}-Suddenly showing up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.54,0:26:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我参观的  第一个博物馆\N{\r原文字幕}It's my first museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.29,0:26:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早就想过会梦到它了\N{\r原文字幕}I thought I might have a dream  about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.42,0:26:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉,亨利,这不是梦\N{\r原文字幕}Sorry, Henry, no.  This isn't a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.63,0:26:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你在这里工作吗?  -我不在这里工作\N{\r原文字幕}-Do you work here?  -No, I don't work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.43,0:26:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些衣服是我偷的  就像我为你偷那件上衣一样\N{\r原文字幕}I stole these clothes  like I stole you that t-shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.47,0:26:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着,我也会时空旅行\N{\r原文字幕}See, I time travel, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.47,0:26:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回到三小时前,我回到‥\N{\r原文字幕}You came back about three hours.  I came back, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.85,0:26:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你说说这是哪一年?  -1987年\N{\r原文字幕}-Remind me, what year is this?  -1987.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.15,0:26:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回到21年前\N{\r原文字幕}Yeah, 21 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.78,0:26:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有很多时空旅人吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Are there lots of time  travelers?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.03,0:27:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家伙,在上面过得如何?\N{\r原文字幕}Hey, big guy.  Hey, how you doing up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.95,0:27:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我搔痒你‥\N{\r原文字幕}Tickle, tickle, tickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.62,0:27:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它不太怕痒呢\N{\r原文字幕}He's not really ticklish,  is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.17,0:27:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想试试吗?  过来吧\N{\r原文字幕}You wanna try? Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.63,0:27:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真没幽默感,难怪都灭绝了\N{\r原文字幕}No sense of humor.  No wonder they all died out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.97,0:27:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么时候会见到  其他时空旅人?\N{\r原文字幕}When do I meet the other ones?  The other time travelers.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.52,0:27:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在饿了吧?\N{\r原文字幕}You're hungry now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.19,0:27:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时空旅行总让人饿肚子,来吧\N{\r原文字幕}Time travel always makes you  hungry. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.91,0:27:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了,吃吧\N{\r原文字幕}Okay. Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.38,0:27:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过不了多久你又会不舒服\N{\r原文字幕}In a minute you're gonna feel  a little sick again
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.13,0:27:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接着就会回到家了,就是这样\N{\r原文字幕}and then you're gonna snap  right back home. That's how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.01,0:28:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\r原文字幕}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.72,0:28:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天开始我会教你\N{\r原文字幕}So. Today's the day,  I'm gonna start teaching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.94,0:28:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的觉得我变得成熟稳重了呢\N{\r原文字幕}I must be feeling very grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.98,0:28:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎么回家?\N{\r原文字幕}How do I get back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.53,0:28:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自然就会回家的\N{\r原文字幕}It'll just happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.78,0:28:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时你不一定会直接回去\N{\r原文字幕}Sometimes you don't go  straight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.57,0:28:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是先到了另一个时空\N{\r原文字幕}You go to another time first.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.28,0:28:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有次我连续去了三个不同的时空\N{\r原文字幕}Once I went  to three different times in a row,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.91,0:28:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但通常你都会直接回家\N{\r原文字幕}but mostly you ping  straight back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.70,0:28:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那我能去未来吗?  -有时可以\N{\r原文字幕}-Can I go to the future, too?  -Yeah. Sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.91,0:28:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不常但还是会发生\N{\r原文字幕}Not so often, but it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.46,0:28:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们怎么办?\N{\r原文字幕}What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.96,0:28:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们怎么办是什么意思?\N{\r原文字幕}What do you mean,  "What do we do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.01,0:28:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是时空旅人  我们会处理犯罪案件吗?\N{\r原文字幕}We're time travelers.  Do we solve crimes?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.47,0:28:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会,亨利,抱歉了\N{\r原文字幕}Uh, no, Henry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.60,0:28:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会处理犯罪案件  而是会犯案\N{\r原文字幕}We don't solve crimes,  we... ...commit them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.60,0:28:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会逃跑,偷窃和战斗\N{\r原文字幕}We run, we steal, we fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.31,0:28:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们时空旅行时  都全身赤裸而且不舒服\N{\r原文字幕}Wherever we show up in time,  we're naked... ...and we're sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.65,0:29:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们别无选择\N{\r原文字幕}We don't get a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.36,0:29:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是坏蛋吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Are we the bad guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.20,0:29:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活下来的通常都是坏蛋\N{\r原文字幕}Survivors are always  the bad guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.78,0:29:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才要教你如何变成大坏蛋\N{\r原文字幕}That's why it's my job, to teach you how to be  the baddest guy out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.66,0:29:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我还会再见到你\N{\r原文字幕}So, I'm gonna see you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.25,0:29:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对,很多次\N{\r原文字幕}Yeah, lots of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.92,0:29:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你保证?  -我保证\N{\r原文字幕}-Do you promise?  -Yeah, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.92,0:29:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实我正好在你这个年纪时\N{\r原文字幕}In fact, when I was your age,  exactly your age,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.68,0:29:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有个人回到那个时刻训练了我\N{\r原文字幕}there was a guy who came back  in time and he trained me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.93,0:29:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在轮到我训练你了\N{\r原文字幕}So now,  it's my turn to train you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.31,0:29:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以有很多我们这种人\N{\r原文字幕}So, there's lots of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.81,0:29:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\r原文字幕}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.14,0:29:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-有我们这种时空旅人很多  -那就好\N{\r原文字幕}There's lots of us  time travelers. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.86,0:29:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会训练你  听起来如何,亨利?\N{\r原文字幕}How does that all sound, Henry?  Me training you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.90,0:29:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可怕\N{\r原文字幕}Scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.70,0:29:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这世界很可怕\N{\r原文字幕}Well, the world's a scary place.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.32,0:29:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你知道要怎么办吗?\N{\r原文字幕}So, you know what you gotta be?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.24,0:29:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得变得更可怕\N{\r原文字幕}You gotta be scarier.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.66,0:29:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等,我突然好像不这么想了\N{\r原文字幕}Yeah, suddenly I'm not sure.  I think that...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.54,0:29:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天还真是成熟稳重的一天啊  我这是怎么了?\N{\r原文字幕}I am having a very grown-up day.  What is up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.13,0:30:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事,你这是要回家了  下次见\N{\r原文字幕}It's okay. You're going home. Next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.72,0:30:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\r原文字幕}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.77,0:30:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死\N{\r原文字幕}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.40,0:30:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死,你们继续,别管我\N{\r原文字幕}Oh, shit. Carry on.  Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.19,0:30:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你在搞什么鬼?  -等我一下‥好吗?\N{\r原文字幕}What the fuck are you doing? Now, just--just give me  a moment, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.28,0:30:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么鬼?\N{\r原文字幕}What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.91,0:30:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能说说现在的日期跟时间吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Yeah. Could you give me the date  and the time, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.20,0:30:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你在说什么?  -我只要日期和时间就好\N{\r原文字幕}-What are you saying?  -Uh, just the date and the fucking time,  that's all I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.08,0:30:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惨了,这波很猛烈\N{\r原文字幕}Oh, shit. This is gonna be  a big one--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.04,0:30:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-6月26日  -谢谢\N{\r原文字幕}-Uh... June 26.  -Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.63,0:30:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-现在晚上8点15分  -闭嘴,别跟他说话\N{\r原文字幕}Yeah, it's 8:15 p.m. Shut up talking to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.68,0:30:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他连衣服都没穿  -2008年?\N{\r原文字幕}He's naked! 2008?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.51,0:30:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧‥我离开了两小时\N{\r原文字幕}Huh, okay, okay. That's uh...I've been gone two hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.56,0:30:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我的衣服不可能还在这里  -你的衣服?\N{\r原文字幕}my clothes won't still be here. Your clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.19,0:31:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你的衣服\N{\r原文字幕}I'm gonna need yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.19,0:31:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你需要什么?\N{\r原文字幕}-You're gonna need what?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.52,0:31:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受伤的会是你,不是我\N{\r原文字幕}-This is gonna hurt. You, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.32,0:31:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天啊\N{\r原文字幕}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.50,0:31:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-丹娜  -丹娜\N{\r原文字幕}-Donna. Uh, Donna.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.00,0:31:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来,我要拿走  你男友的衣服后离开\N{\r原文字幕}What's gonna happen now  is I'm gonna take your boyfriend's clothes  and just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.80,0:31:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以把他摆好位置让他休息  并且报警\N{\r原文字幕}If you like, you can put him  in the recovery position and call the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.93,0:31:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能向他们描述我\N{\r原文字幕}Give them  my description by all means,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.01,0:31:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我全身赤裸  你会发现竟然难以记得细节\N{\r原文字幕}but I'm naked, you'll find  details surprisingly difficult to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.68,0:31:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些花是他送你的吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Did he give you those flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.27,0:31:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-对  -真好\N{\r原文字幕}-Yeah.  -Oh, that's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.65,0:31:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他看起来不像这种人\N{\r原文字幕}He doesn't seem like the type.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.65,0:31:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然他挺混蛋而且约会也毁了\N{\r原文字幕}Seeing as he's kind  of an asshole and this is a shitty date anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.07,0:31:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,介意我拿走花吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Mind if I take them?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.24,0:31:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我赴约已经迟到了\N{\r原文字幕}I'm late for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.91,0:31:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你好  -你好,你从来不曾送我花\N{\r原文字幕}-Hi.  -Hi. You've never brought me  flowers before.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.53,0:31:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你觉得花有用吗?  -不是,我只是认为‥\N{\r原文字幕}-Do you think that's gonna work?  -No, I just think
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.37,0:32:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花能为你的公寓增色\N{\r原文字幕}that your apartment  might be a bit nicer.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.92,0:32:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你的公寓不好吗?  -那是我住的公寓\N{\r原文字幕}-Well, what's wrong with yours?  -Well, I live in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.46,0:32:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的生活乱七八糟  乱到像是一处养着人的农场\N{\r原文字幕}I live really badly in it,  it's like a farm for one human.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.09,0:32:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好笑,我认识你这么久了\N{\r原文字幕}You know it's funny,  I've known you almost all my life
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.26,0:32:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你却和我想象的不太一样\N{\r原文字幕}and you're not what  I was expecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.18,0:32:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我让你失望了?  -不是‥\N{\r原文字幕}Am I a disappointment? No, no. Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.81,0:32:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只是‥很独特\N{\r原文字幕}you're just uh-- Well, you're different.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.02,0:32:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的还是坏的独特?\N{\r原文字幕}Well, different good or bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.48,0:32:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是很独特\N{\r原文字幕}Just different.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.27,0:32:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧,变得更糟糕了\N{\r原文字幕}Oh, no. It's got a lot worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.99,0:32:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你数数到一百万\N{\r原文字幕}You are gonna have to count  to a million.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.20,0:32:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,85,86,87,88  89,90\N{\r原文字幕}Eighty-five,  86, 87... ...88, 89, 90,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.00,0:32:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-快点  -继续数数\N{\r原文字幕}hurry up. -Keep counting.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.58,0:32:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-天啊,都十四年了  -快点数数\N{\r原文字幕}-Jesus! Fourteen years. Count, come on.  Count, count, count.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.81,0:33:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你人还在吗?\N{\r原文字幕}-You still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.94,0:33:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对,再一分钟,快数数\N{\r原文字幕}-Yeah, one more minute. -Count, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.52,0:33:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,90‥我数到哪边‥97,98\N{\r原文字幕} -Ninety--I mean where? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.53,0:33:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,99,100,101,102\N{\r原文字幕}-99, 100.  -Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.78,0:34:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这才不是大人的公寓\N{\r原文字幕}This is not the apartment  of a grown-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.91,0:34:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说不公平\N{\r原文字幕}Oh, that's not fair.
